snippet.title: Tales of Symphonia Remastered | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Follow Lloyd and friends on their journey through the world of Sylvarant in HD! 

Tales of Symphonia Remastered will officially release February 17th, 2023 with improved graphics and gameplay for PS4, Xbox One, and Nintendo Switch. 
*Footage shown may differ from the final version of the game.

Pre-order today: https://bnent.eu/TOSRpreorder

Follow us on:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/talesofseries/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TalesofSeries
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/tales/
Web: https://www.talesofarise.com

#TALESOFSYMPHONIA #TALESOF
